Hi @iamyuiwong , are you using the pipeline to start streaming?
If so,please note that you should pass a `rs2::config` instance to the `pipeline.start(cfg)` method. For example:
```cpp
rs2::config cfg;
rs2::pipeline pipe;
cfg.enable_device(sr300_serial);
pipe.strat(cfg);
```
This will only start streaming with the specified sr300 camera. If you call `pipe.strat()` (without passing the config object, then the default configuration will be chosen and D435 will start streaming if it is connected.

If you are not using the pipeline, please post the code you use and we'll see what you are missing.

